Module jdk.jshell
Package jdk.jshell

Enum Snippet.SubKind

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Snippet.SubKind>
jdk.jshell.Snippet.SubKind
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Snippet.SubKind>, Constable
Enclosing class:
Snippet
public static enum Snippet.SubKind
extends Enum<Snippet.SubKind>
The detailed variety of a snippet. This is a sub-classification of the Kind. The Kind of a SubKind is accessible with kind().
